an></strong><br />\n香港正受人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n公然妨礙新聞自由 警方出公關稿籲媒體跟從<br />\n截斷交通 封鎖去道<br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span></span><br />\n實彈已出 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<br />\n召喚攬炒巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753d2f69faff95190f4aafeb4a3342c724d81f40","tid":1527043,"uid":84741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:48:32.000Z","msg":"太子啲手足去晒邊"},{"pid":"bf01a6600848510f4d76b2aa7d8caeb0f2973631","tid":1527043,"uid":92383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"308b4323b1c1d1e80058e355f47d9eb76eb53245","tid":1527043,"uid":275884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:54:08.000Z","msg":"香港人！我哋需要改變生活習慣救香港呀！<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dKJOcT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dKJOcT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}